        <dc:date>2019-09-20T15:05:14+00:00</dc:date>
        <dc:description>&lt;div&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Learn Ethereum is ideal for anyone who wants to quickly learn Ethereum blockchain technology and build end-to-end decentralized applications using smart contract and Ethereum. The hands-on examples will help novices learn quick, effective, and easy ways to master blockchain and Ethereum. Prior exposure to an object-oriented programming language such as JavaScript is expected but is not mandatory.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</dc:description>
